metadata.description:
[#001 Awaken]
Swallowtail butterflies are a mixture of humbleness, struggle, fragile, fantasy, metamorphosis and beauty.
Like we humans, struggling for survival and dreams. Sometimes stuck in mud while love and kind-hearted give us the wings of angels that could fly like swallowtail butterflies in the sunshine.

--

[CYBER BUTTERFLY INTRODUCTION]
The inspiration for Cyber butterfly is from Shunji Iwai’s movie Swallowtail butterfly. It touched me a lot when I first saw it as a teenager.
For a while I suddenly remembered some touched scenes and watch this movie again.
Memory’s amazing sometimes, it could be reminded by a small details and welling out with a lot of related things.
